GETOFF02 CLI   PPREL,0                                                          
         JE    EXITY                                                            
         CLI   PPREL,PPRELQ                                                     
         JE    GETOFF04                                                         
         LLC   R0,PPRLN                                                         
         AR    R3,R0                                                            
         J     GETOFF02                                                         
                                                                                
GETOFF04 CLC   PPRGAOFF,SPACES                                                  
         JNH   EXITY                                                            
         MVC   X#SJOFF,PPRGAOFF                                                 
