         JNE   FLTRECN                                        estimate          
                                                                                
         CLI   RQ_ESCLS,NOQ        Do we want no closed jobs                    
         JNE   *+12                                                             
         CLI   X#TEMP+38,YESQ      If job is closed skip this estimate          
         JE    FLTRECN                                                          
                                                                                
