         JE    LLSUSE25                                                         
                                                                                
LLSUSE30 CLI   K.GAPTDAT1,GAPTT5Q                                               
         JNE   LLSUSE10                                                         
         CLC   K.GAPTACT,SPACES    if 1st entry is spaces                       
