         JE    ELFBLL18                                                         
         GOTOR (#GOATSR,AGOATSR),DMCB,('TSANXT',ATSRERRS),0,GAPAREA,   +        
               TSARABUF            skip all other types                         
         J     ELFBLL16                                                         
