ELFBLL22 CLI   BYTE3,1             client?                                      
         JE    ELFBLL25                                                         
         OI    BYTE2,X'80'         matched at client level                      
         AHI   RF,1                                                             
         AR    R6,RF                                                            
         LLC   RE,PPROLEN                                                       
         SR    RE,RF                                                            
         SHI   RE,1                                                             
         BASR  R1,0                                                             
         CLC   0(0,R6),ELFPRO                                                   
         EX    RE,0(R1)                                                         
